‚Üíapp.use(): Adds middleware to the pipeline and allows passing control to the next middleware.
->app. Map(): Grease branches in the pipeline for specific paths.
->app. Run(): Adds terminal middleware, no futher middleware is  executed of after this.

3.)Can you explain how Middleware is ordered in the pipeline?

‚ÜíMiddleware is executed in the order it's registered. in program.cs order matters becausa later middleware depends on earlier ones.

