üî• **Top 50 Web API Interview Questions**

for .NET Developers üë®‚Äçüíªüë©‚Äçüíª

Are you preparing for interviews in **.NET / ASP.NET Core Web API**?
These **frequently asked questions** will help you **crack your next tech round** confidently! üí•

üìå **Basics of Web API**

‚ñ™Ô∏è What is Web API?
‚ñ™Ô∏è Difference between Web API and WCF?
‚ñ™Ô∏è Difference between Web API and REST API?
‚ñ™Ô∏è What are the HTTP methods supported in Web API?
‚ñ™Ô∏è What is REST? Key principles?
‚ñ™Ô∏è PUT vs PATCH ‚Äì what's the difference?
‚ñ™Ô∏è Common HTTP status codes?
‚ñ™Ô∏è 200 OK vs 201 Created vs 204 No Content
‚ñ™Ô∏è 400 Bad Request vs 404 Not Found
‚ñ™Ô∏è What is Media Type Formatter?

