üéØ Top .NET Core MVC Interview Questions Asked by TCS, Infosys, Accenture, Capgemini, LTI, Cognizant, Deloitte & More!


‚úÖ 1‚Äì10: Basics of .NET Core MVC
1. What is .NET Core and how is it different from .NET Framework?
